  <brief_title>Assessment of Grazax® Treatment Compliance</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Parallel-Group, Open, Controlled Phase III Trial Assessing the Treatment Compliance With GRAZAX® in Subjects With Seasonal Grass Pollen Induced Rhinoconjunctivitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
